        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-0 fade-in-up delay-1500">
            We've reimagined gym management software from the ground up. Slate isn't just a toolâ€”it's the complete operating system for modern climbing facilities. Unified, intuitive, and designed to help your community thrive.
